{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "六月初八夜，十二连环坞总舵大厅中，三批人马汇报调查结果。熊天健率队回太行山小镇调查无果，叶星士追查善使刀的名家也无线索，王毅的收获有限。鹰眼老七亲自前往沿海查访，得知陆小凤已随老狐狸的船出海且船已沉没，全员遇难。面对世子的七天限期，众人束手无策，鹰眼老七自嘲建议大家一头撞死。次日清晨，陆小凤从小老头密室出来，想找岳洋却遇见沙曼。沙曼引他到小屋，两人发生亲密关系。醒来后沙曼问起飞天玉虎，透露飞天玉虎真名江玉飞，自己原名江沙曼，两人是兄妹。沙曼曾发誓以身体酬谢杀死飞天玉虎的人，陆小凤发现她是为了复仇。经过一番对话，两人感情升温，沙曼挽留陆小凤。此时有人高呼九少爷回来了，沙曼惊慌，陆小凤故作洒脱。九公子悄然留下一朵冰花后离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "镖师们投宿的那客栈叫悦来，因为地方偏僻，土地不值钱，所以客栈建造得很宽阔，一共有三十九间客房。",
      "tone": "汇报",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们已将三十九间客房内每一寸的地方都仔细搜查过，并没有血迹，也没有兵刃暗器留下来的痕迹，可以说完全没有可疑之处。",
      "tone": "汇报",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当地一共有一百七十八户人家，大多是土生土长的，每一家我们都去问过，出事前后几天，附近都没有看见过可疑的人。",
      "tone": "汇报",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_tian_jian",
      "speaker_name": "熊天健",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "惟一可疑的地方是，出事前的那天早上，有一批木匠到过那里，带着几大车木材，据说是为了要做佛像和木鱼用的。",
      "tone": "汇报",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆小凤已出海远行，只怕永远不会回来了。",
      "tone": "泄气",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们有没有看见过一个长着四条眉毛的人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "狐狸窝的人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "那个人也在我们老板的那条船上。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是遇难沉没的那条船？",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "狐狸窝的人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们有个法子。",
      "tone": "提议",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家都在这里一头撞死。",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假如我要睡觉，应该到哪里去睡？",
      "tone": "自语",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老朋友那大肚子里，是不是也有个人？这个人没有牛肉汤喝，是不是已经死了？",
      "tone": "自语",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你杀了飞天玉虎？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你认得他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他的真名叫江玉飞，我本来叫江沙曼。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你们是兄妹么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "应答",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我能够活到现在，已经是运气，能够死在这样的女人手里，也算是运气，我还有什么好埋怨的？",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "我虽然没有亲手杀死他，他却是因我而死的，假如我有第二次机会，说不定会亲手杀了他。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我曾经不止一次发过誓，无论谁杀了他，我都要将自己的身体作为酬谢，我已没有什么别的法子能表达我的感激。",
      "tone": "悲哀",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他虽然是我的哥哥，却害了我一生。",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我答应过自己的事，现在我做到了，你也可以走了。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "我不走。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你还要什么？难道还要一次？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仆人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九少爷回来了，九少爷回来了。",
      "tone": "高呼",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你不妨先走，我很快就会走的，今天的事，我一定也很快就会忘记。",
      "tone": "勉强",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你一定要我先走？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你可以不必走。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "欲言又止",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我做的事并不怕别人知道，你随便在这里呆多久都没关系。",
      "tone": "奇怪",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "我有样东西送给你，不知道你肯不肯要？",
      "tone": "笑着",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你要送的是什么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "我的夜壶刀。",
      "tone": "幽默",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不要走。",
      "tone": "柔情",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "嘶哑",
      "chapter": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我……我不要你走。",
      "tone": "柔情",
      "chapter": 8
    }
  ],
